<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201121/aead2ae563f1494189fa203e0504d340.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">语文听课现场</span></img></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
